question: List script supervisors and costume designers that are 45 years old.
sql_query1:
SELECT Script_Supervisors.name
FROM Script_Supervisors
WHERE Script_Supervisors.Age = 45
UNION
SELECT Costume_Designers.name
FROM Costume_Designers
WHERE Costume_Designers.Age = 45
sql_query2:
SELECT Script_Supervisors.name
FROM Script_Supervisors
UNION
SELECT Costume_Designers.name
FROM Costume_Designers
WHERE Costume_Designers.Age = 45
interpretation1: Which script supervisors are 45 years old and which costume designers are at the same age?
interpretation2: Provide the list of all script supervisors and also provide a list of costume designers that are 45 years old.
